\end_inset

 m.s
\begin_inset Formula $^{-1}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
3.
 The smallest wavenumber of the flow is 
\begin_inset Formula $k=\frac{2\pi}{L_{C}}$
